Group A.
Species with lateral vitelline fields continuous in the ventral sucker area, oblique to tandem testes and cirrus-sac not normally extending posterior to the ventral sucker:
Macvicaria alacris (Looss, 1901) Gibson & Bray, 1982
;
M. soleae ( Nicoll, 1910 ) Gibson & Bray, 1982
;
M. microtestis Zdzitowiecki & Cielecka, 1997
;
M. oligolecithosus ( Wang, Wang & Zhang, 1992 )
n. comb.

